I"v<ol>
  <li>On boot, press <code class="highlighter-rouge">cmd + S</code> to enter single user mode.</li>
  <li>Run
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>mount <span class="nt">-uw</span> /
<span class="nb">rm</span> /var/db/.AppleSetupDone
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Continue boot process by pressing <code class="highlighter-rouge">ctrl + D</code>.</li>
  <li>Finish the setup wizard to create a new admin user.</li>
</ol>

